'''阿什莉·布拉泽·拜登'''（{{lang-en|Ashley Blazer Biden}}，{{bd|1981年|6月8日||}}），美国社会工作者、社运人士、慈善家、时装设计师，為[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]的女儿。2014年至2019年任特拉华州司法中心执行主任。在中心任公职前，供职于{{tsl|en|Delaware Department of Services for Children, Youth, and Their Families|特拉华州儿童、青年及其家属服务部}}。另外还于2017年[[纽约时装周|纽约时装周]]宣布成立时装公司Livelihood，与网络零售商{{tsl|en|Gilt Groupe|吉尔特集团}}共同为社区计划募资，从而消除国内收入不平等现象。

== 早年与家庭 ==
1981年6月8日，阿什莉·拜登在[[特拉华州|特拉华州]][[威尔明顿_(特拉华州)|威尔明顿]]出生<ref name="ap-timeline">{{cite news | url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/n/a/2008/08/22/politics/p222636D16.DTL | title=Timeline of Biden's life and career | publisher=Associated Press | date=2008-08-23 | access-date=2008-09-06 | archive-date=2008-09-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080925021142/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fn%2Fa%2F2008%2F08%2F22%2Fpolitics%2Fp222636D16.DTL | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.popsugar.com/node/47463956|title=Get to Know All of Joe Biden's Kids and Grandkids!|first=Hedy|last=Phillips|date=2020-05-14|website=POPSUGAR Family}}</ref>。其父[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]系前[[美国副总统|美国副总统]]、现任[[美国总统当选人|当选总统]]，其母[[吉尔·拜登|吉尔·拜登]]是教育家<ref name= wedding>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/03/fashion/weddings/ashley-biden-howard-krein-wedding.html|title=Ashley Biden and Howard Krein (Published 2012)|date=2012-06-03|via=NYTimes.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101001405/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/03/fashion/weddings/ashley-biden-howard-krein-wedding.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[亨特·拜登|亨特·拜登]]及已故的[[博·拜登|博·拜登]]由乔·拜登和前妻[[内莉亚·亨特|内莉亚·亨特·拜登]]所生，是她同父异母的哥哥<ref name= heavy>{{Cite web|url=https://heavy.com/news/2020/08/ashley-biden/|title=Ashley Biden, Joe's Daughter: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know|first=Jessica|last=McBride|date=2020-08-21|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101064656/https://heavy.com/news/2020/08/ashley-biden/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.marieclaire.com/politics/a32389157/ashley-biden-joe-biden-daughter/|title=Joe Biden's Youngest Daughter, Ashley, Lives the Most Low-Key Life of His Kids|first=Katherine J.|last=Igoe|date=2020-09-28|website=Marie Claire|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102154248/https://www.marieclaire.com/politics/a32389157/ashley-biden-joe-biden-daughter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曾祖父是{{tsl|en|Edward Francis Blewitt|爱德华·弗朗西斯·布莱维特}}<ref>{{cite news |url=https://news.lafayette.edu/2012/05/03/vice-president-joe-biden-discusses-american-innovation/ |title=Vice President Joe Biden Discusses American Innovation |last=Gehman |first=Geoff |publisher=Lafayette College |date=2012-05-03 |access-date=2020-04-15 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927014954/https://news.lafayette.edu/2012/05/03/vice-president-joe-biden-discusses-american-innovation/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿什莉继承了父亲的英国、法国和爱尔兰血统，也有母亲的英国、苏格兰和[[西西里人|西西里]]血统<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://irishamerica.com/2013/03/joey-from-scranton-vice-president-bidens-irish-roots/|title=Joey From Scranton: VP Biden's Irish Roots|date=2013-03-20|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023021031/https://irishamerica.com/2013/03/joey-from-scranton-vice-president-bidens-irish-roots/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://archive.org/details/isbn_9780061791987|title=Joe Biden : a life of trial and redemption|first=Jules|last=Witcover|date=2010-10-11|publisher=New York : William Morrow/HarperCollins|via=Internet Archive}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/05/31/AR2009053102568.html|title=Obamas' Chow: Politically Palatable|first=Amy Argetsinger and Roxanne|last=Roberts|date=2009-06-01|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013110201/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/05/31/AR2009053102568.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿什莉随家人信仰[[天主教|天主教]]，在[[特拉华州|特拉华州]][[格林维尔_(特拉华州)|格林维尔]]受洗<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/daughter-of-us-vice-president-marries/|title=Biden's daughter marries into the tribe|website=timesofisrael.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101071847/https://www.timesofisrael.com/daughter-of-us-vice-president-marries/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://people.com/celebrity/joe-biden-daughter-ashley-biden-howard-krein-wed/|title=Joe Biden Daughter, Ashley Biden, Howard Krein Wed|website=PEOPLE.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030011839/https://people.com/celebrity/joe-biden-daughter-ashley-biden-howard-krein-wed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。年少时，父亲是特拉华州的国会参议员，母亲是教育家<ref name= today/><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Politico|date=2014-12-18|title=Women Rule Keynote: Vice President Joe Biden|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x0rCpsC1onE&feature=youtu.be&t=302|access-date=2020-10-11|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107131515/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x0rCpsC1onE&feature=youtu.be&t=302|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

