阿什莉小学就读于[[貴格會|貴格會]]在威尔明顿经营的私立学校{{tsl|en|Wilmington Friends School|威尔明顿贵格会学校}}<ref name=cpb>{{cite interview|url=https://cpb-us-w2.wpmucdn.com/sites.udel.edu/dist/4/10696/files/2018/01/advocating-for-justice-and-equality-an-interview-with-ashley-biden-2al8eyv.pdf|title=Advocating for Justice and Equality: An Interview with Ashley Biden|first=Ashley|last=Biden|interviewer=M. Kristen Hefner|work=New Visions for Public Affairs|publisher=School of Public Policy and Adminsitration, University of Delaware|date=Spring 2014|volume=6|pages=5–11|format=PDF|access-date=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031034945/https://cpb-us-w2.wpmucdn.com/sites.udel.edu/dist/4/10696/files/2018/01/advocating-for-justice-and-equality-an-interview-with-ashley-biden-2al8eyv.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0" /><ref name= rutgers/>。1999年，于私立天主教学校{{tsl|en|Archmere Academy|阿奇米尔学院}}中学毕业（这里也是乔·拜登的母校）<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-11-12|title=Joseph R. Biden '61 Becomes First Auk Elected as President of the United States|url=https://www.archmereacademy.com/News-Detail?pk=1241181|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119044520/https://www.archmereacademy.com/News-Detail?pk=1241181|archive-date=2020-11-19|access-date=2020-11-19|website=Archmere Academy|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾加入学校的[[袋棍球|袋棍球]]和[[草地曲棍球|草地曲棍球]]队<ref name= thelist/>。阿什莉还是小学生的时候，有一次曾了解到美妆产品公司{{tsl|en|Bonne Bell|Bonne Bell}}用动物测试产品，于是写信给这家公司，要求他们更改有关政策<ref name= elle/>。之后参与[[海豚|海豚]]保育，启发乔·拜登和国会议员[[芭芭拉·柏克瑟|芭芭拉·柏克瑟]]起草获通过的《1990年海豚保护消费者知情法》（1990 Dolphin Protection Consumer Information Act）<ref name= today>{{Cite web|url=https://delawaretoday.com/life-style/ashley-biden-takes-on-the-world/|title=Ashley Biden Takes On The World|date=2018-08-22|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101012809/https://delawaretoday.com/life-style/ashley-biden-takes-on-the-world/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而阿什莉也曾在[[美国国会|美国国会]]议员面前就该法进行游说<ref name= elle/>。

== 教育经历与职业生涯 ==
阿什莉于[[杜兰大学|杜兰大学]]学习[[文化人类学|文化人类学]]<ref name= wedding/>。大一那年，她加入女子公司（Girls Incorporated，今金斯伍德学院（Kingswood Academy）），担任夏令营顾问<ref name= cpb/>。她还参加[[乔治城大学|乔治城大学]]的夏令营计划，与{{le|阿纳科斯|Anacostia}}的年轻人一起工作<ref name= cpb/>。毕业后，她在威尔明顿的一家披萨店打了几个月零工，当服务员，随后开始社会工作的职业生涯<ref name=":0" />。她搬到[[费城|费城]]{{le|肯辛顿 (费城)|Kensington, Philadelphia|肯辛顿}}，在西北人士服务儿童专科诊所（Northwestern Human Services Children's Reach Clinic）担任临床支持专家，帮助年青人和他们的家人获取资源，直接和精神科医生和治疗师一起工作<ref name= cpb/><ref name=":0" /><ref name= newsbreak>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newsbreak.com/people/ashley-biden|title=Ashley Biden - Biography & News|website=News Break|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101054942/https://www.newsbreak.com/people/ashley-biden|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，阿什莉获得[[宾夕法尼亚大学|宾夕法尼亚大学]]{{le|宾夕法尼亚大学社会政策与实践学院|University of Pennsylvania School of Social Policy and Practice|社会政策与实践学院}}社会工作硕士学位<ref name= rutgers>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rutgers.edu/news/ashley-biden-daughter-vice-president-speak-rutgers-school-social-work-convocation|title=Ashley Biden, Daughter of the Vice President, to Speak at Rutgers' School of Social Work Convocation|website=rutgers.edu|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101051938/https://www.rutgers.edu/news/ashley-biden-daughter-vice-president-speak-rutgers-school-social-work-convocation|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name= elle>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elle.com/culture/career-politics/a33645978/who-is-ashley-biden-joe-biden-daughter/|title=All About Ashley Biden, Joe's Youngest Daughter With a Civically-Minded Fashion Label|first=Savannah|last=Walsh|date=2020-08-19|website=Elle|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105120558/https://www.elle.com/culture/career-politics/a33645978/who-is-ashley-biden-joe-biden-daughter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她是{{le|约翰·霍普·富兰克林|John Hope Franklin}}美国种族主义斗争奖（Combating American Racism Award）获奖毕业生，共有12人获该殊荣<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.inquirer.com/philly/news/local/20100518_At_Penn__Biden_speaks_at_daughter_s_graduation.html|title=At Penn, Biden speaks at daughter's graduation|first=By Claudia Vargas, Inquirer Staff|last=Writer|website=inquirer.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101224918/https://www.inquirer.com/philly/news/local/20100518_At_Penn__Biden_speaks_at_daughter_s_graduation.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 社会活动 ===
阿什莉是社会正义活动人士、社会工作者<ref name= thelist>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thelist.com/176589/ashley-bidens-transformation-is-seriously-turning-heads/|title=Ashley Biden's transformation is seriously turning heads|first=Kelsie|last=Calderon|date=2019-11-26|website=TheList.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102050640/https://www.thelist.com/176589/ashley-bidens-transformation-is-seriously-turning-heads/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。研究生毕业后，她加入非营利组织西区邻舍（West End Neighborhood House），担任刑满出狱青年就业与教育联络员，负责筹划就业和职业技能培训计划<ref name= cpb/><ref name=":0" /><ref name= newsbreak/>。她也在{{tsl|en|Delaware Department of Services for Children, Youth, and Their Families|特拉华州儿童、青年及其家属服务部}}社工共15年<ref name= elle/><ref name= wedding/>。任职期间，她就少年司法、寄养和心理健康问题制订了多项计划<ref name= elle/>。2008年，她被《特拉华州今日》（''Delaware Today''）列为“四十大杰出人士”（40 People to Watch）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://delawaretoday.com/uncategorized/40-people-to-watch/|first=Matt|last=Amis|title=40 People to Watch|work=Delaware Today|date=2008-05-23|access-date=2020-10-14|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018220505/https://delawaretoday.com/uncategorized/40-people-to-watch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年加入特拉华州司法中心（Delaware Center for Justice），任助理主任，负责该州的刑法改革问题<ref name= elle/><ref name= today/><ref name= heavy/>，以及公共教育、成年受害人服务、枪支暴力、妇女囚犯及社区在融入方面的服务工作<ref name=cpb/>。她还负责监督中心的所有直接服务计划，接待需要接受感化的犯罪受害者、刑满出狱青年、年长囚犯、缓刑假释成年囚犯、逃学青年及{{tsl|en|Pennsylvania courts of common pleas|宾夕法尼亚州普通法院}}客户<ref name= cpb/>。2014年晋升中心执行主任，2019年辞职<ref name= elle/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.oprahmag.com/life/a33656664/joe-biden-children/|title=How Joe Biden's Children Have Inspired and Carried on His Political Legacy|first=Grant|last=Rindner|date=2020-08-20|website=Oprah Magazine|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110175239/https://www.oprahmag.com/life/a33656664/joe-biden-children/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她推出的学生反枪支与黑帮勇士（Student Warriors Against Guns and Gangs）计划获{{tsl|en|Office of Juvenile Justice and Delinquency Prevention|少年司法和预防犯罪办公室}}采用，用来提供教育资源和社区志愿团体，消除[[纽卡斯尔县|纽卡斯尔县]]的暴力犯罪和帮派活动<ref name= cpb/>。

[[File:Ashley_Biden_Plays_Games_With_South_African_Children_(4690981899).jpg|thumb]]马佩特拉日托中心（Mapetla Day Care Centre）儿童交流，摄于2010年6月的外访活动]]
2014年，阿什莉批评[[美国死刑制度|死刑制度]]，表示这种惩罚不划算，浪费了可以用来服务受害者和预防犯罪的资源<ref name= cpb/>。她成立青年@艺术（Young@Art）计划，为在囚学生提供艺术品创作的资源和平台，在社区出售他们的作品<ref name= cpb/>。艺术品所获收益的一半归于艺术创作者，一半收归计划，用来购买美术用品及向参与社区艺术展的青年支付薪水<ref name= cpb/>。她还利用这项计划，向学生教授商务和金融知识的技能<ref name= cpb/>。

=== 时装 ===
2017年[[纽约时装周|纽约时装周]]，阿什莉在[[翠贝卡|翠贝卡]]春天广场（Spring Place）宣布公益时装品牌Livelihood Collection<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/02/08/fashion/joe-biden-gilt-fashion-week.html|title=Joe Biden Drops by a Fashion Party. The Reason? His Daughter. (Published 2017)|first=Valeriya|last=Safronova|date=2017-02-08|via=NYTimes.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001024836/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/02/08/fashion/joe-biden-gilt-fashion-week.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name= elle/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.glamour.com/story/ashley-biden-sweatshirt-line-livelihood-is-style-with-social-conscience|title=Ashley Biden's New Sweatshirt Line Is Style With a Powerful Social Conscience|first=Leah|last=Bourne|website=Glamour}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.womenshealthmag.com/life/a32389803/joe-biden-children/|title=Everything You Need To Know About Joe Biden's Four Children Before Tonight's Debate|first=Emily|last=Shiffer|date=2020-09-29|website=Women's Health|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118091631/https://www.womenshealthmag.com/life/a32389803/joe-biden-children/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的父母、[[奧莉維亞·巴勒莫|奧莉維亞·巴勒莫]]和{{tsl|en|Christian Siriano|克里斯蒂安·西里亚诺}}等名人出席品牌发布会<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://graziadaily.co.uk/celebrity/news/joe-bidens-fashion-designer-ashley-daughter-livelihood-collection/|title=Joe Biden's Fashion Designer Daughter Just Raised The Normcore Bar|website=Grazia}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://guestofaguest.com/new-york/events/joe-biden-takes-over-new-york-fashion-week-with-gilt|title=Joe Biden Takes Over New York Fashion Week With Gilt|website=Guest of a Guest|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015080445/https://guestofaguest.com/new-york/events/joe-biden-takes-over-new-york-fashion-week-with-gilt|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该品牌与{{tsl|en|Gilt Groupe|Gilt集团}}和[[奧布瑞·克莉絲丁·普拉扎|奧布瑞·克莉絲丁·普拉扎]]合作，为{{tsl|en|Delaware Community Foundation|特拉华州社区基金会}}募资3万美元<ref name= elle/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.usmagazine.com/stylish/news/former-vp-joe-biden-supports-daughter-ashley-at-fashion-week-w465793/|title=Joe Biden Supports Daughter Ashley at Her NYFW Debut!|date=2017-02-08|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016222630/https://www.usmagazine.com/stylish/news/former-vp-joe-biden-supports-daughter-ashley-at-fashion-week-w465793/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wusa9.com/article/entertainment/entertainment-tonight/joe-biden-supports-daughter-ashleys-debut-at-new-york-fashion-week-see-the-adorable-pics/65-404666224|title=Joe Biden Supports Daughter Ashley's Debut at New York Fashion Week -- See the Adorable Pics!|website=wusa9.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017045907/https://www.wusa9.com/article/entertainment/entertainment-tonight/joe-biden-supports-daughter-ashleys-debut-at-new-york-fashion-week-see-the-adorable-pics/65-404666224|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。品牌的商标为一支箭穿过字母“LH”，灵感出自2015年脑癌去世的同父异母哥哥博<ref name= lily/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://technical.ly/delaware/2017/02/09/ashley-biden-livelihood-launch/|title=Here's what went down at the NYC launch of Ashley Biden's charitable clothing line|first=Tony Abraham /|last=contributor|date=2017-02-09|website=Technical.ly Delaware|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101150348/https://technical.ly/delaware/2017/02/09/ashley-biden-livelihood-launch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿什莉创立该品牌，希望对付美国的收入和种族不平等问题<ref name= elle/><ref name= today/>。品牌发布会的全部收益将捐给弱势群体计划<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/national-international/joe-biden-supports-daughter-ashley-new-york-fashion-week-event/2055406/|title=Former Vice President Joe Biden Supports Daughter Ashley's New York Fashion Week Event|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107222455/https://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/national-international/joe-biden-supports-daughter-ashley-new-york-fashion-week-event/2055406/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last=Nguyen | first=Diana | title=Ashley Biden Makes Her Fashion Designer Debut in a Hoodie | website=E! Online | date=2017-02-08 | url=https://www.eonline.com/news/827521/joe-biden-s-daughter-ashley-biden-makes-her-fashion-designer-debut-in-an-awesome-hoodie | access-date=2020-11-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/national-international/joe-biden-supports-daughter-ashley-new-york-fashion-week-event/2031274/|title=Former Vice President Joe Biden Supports Daughter Ashley's New York Fashion Week Event}}</ref>，后续销售所得利润的10%会捐给华盛顿特区阿纳科斯社区和威尔明顿河谷镇的社区组织<ref name= lily/>。产品采用原产自美国的有机棉花，在美国制造<ref name= eco>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ecowatch.com/ashley-biden-livelihood-2259220668.html|title=Ashley Biden Shows Ivanka Trump How to Make American Fashion Great Again|date=2017-02-13|website=EcoWatch|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003932/https://www.ecowatch.com/ashley-biden-livelihood-2259220668.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name= teenvogue>{{Cite web|url=https://www.teenvogue.com/story/ashley-biden-partners-with-gilt-on-livelihood-clothing-line|title=Joe Biden's Daughter Launched Clothing That's ACTUALLY Made in the U.S.|first=Melanie|last=Mignucci|website=Teen Vogue|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111213454/https://www.teenvogue.com/story/ashley-biden-partners-with-gilt-on-livelihood-clothing-line|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她决定给品牌设计[[连帽衫|连帽衫]]，考虑到他们和[[劳工运动|劳工运动]]的联系，以及对社会正义的标志性意义<ref name= eco/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.today.com/style/ashley-biden-joe-biden-s-daughter-launches-new-hoodie-line-t108034|title=How Joe Biden's daughter is giving back with her new hoodie line|website=TODAY.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112155432/https://www.today.com/style/ashley-biden-joe-biden-s-daughter-launches-new-hoodie-line-t108034|dead-url=no}}</ref>。品牌网站还提供公民参与和经济正义方面的信息<ref name= eco/><ref name= teenvogue/>。

阿什莉与[[柯琳·艾特伍|柯琳·艾特伍]]、{{tsl|en|Barbara Tfank|芭芭拉·特芬克}}、{{tsl|en|Rachel Zoe|蕾切尔·佐伊}}、{{tsl|en|Bibhu Mohapatra|比布·莫哈帕特拉}}、{{tsl|en|Betsey Johnson|贝西·约翰逊}}、[[卡爾文·克雷恩_(設計師)|卡尔文·克莱恩]]、[[奥斯卡·德拉伦塔|奥斯卡·德拉伦塔]]、[[萧志美|萧志美]]、{{tsl|en|Paul Tazewell|保罗·塔兹韦尔}}等设计师一起为《[[花生漫画|花生漫画]]》角色[[史努比|史努比]]和贝儿的12英寸塑料娃娃设计衣服，他们的作品于2017年9月7日在[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]][[布魯克菲爾德廣場_(紐約)|布魯克菲爾德廣場]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/will-joe-biden-run-in-2020-his-designer-daughter-ashley-sure-hopes-so-10973384/|title=Will Joe Biden Run in 2020? His Designer Daughter Ashley Sure Hopes So|first1=Rosemary|last1=Feitelberg|date=2017-09-07|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115012729/https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/will-joe-biden-run-in-2020-his-designer-daughter-ashley-sure-hopes-so-10973384/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://therecessionista.com/new-snoopy-belle-exhibit-at-ny-fashion-week-features-hamilton/|title=New Snoopy and Belle Exhibit features Hamilton Costumes|date=2017-09-07|website=The Recessionista®}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vogue.com/article/snoopy-belle-brookfield-place-exhibition-new-york-fashion-week-party|title=Snoopy and Belle's Fashion Exhibition Party at Brookfield Place|first=Condé|last=Nast|website=Vogue|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017000019/https://www.vogue.com/article/snoopy-belle-brookfield-place-exhibition-new-york-fashion-week-party|dead-url=no}}</ref>开始的“史努比和贝尔时装展”（''Snoopy and Belle in Fashion''）展出<ref name= apparel>{{Cite web|url=http://www.apparelnews.net/news/2017/sep/14/snoopys-fashion-tour/|title=Snoopy's Fashion Tour|website=apparelnews.net|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011232929/http://www.apparelnews.net/news/2017/sep/14/snoopys-fashion-tour/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.snoopyandbelleinfashion.com/|title=Snoopy and Belle In Fashion|website=Snoopy and Belle In Fashion|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115080000/http://www.snoopyandbelleinfashion.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.artsbrookfield.com/event/snoopy/|title=Snoopy & Belle in Fashion|website=Arts Brookfield|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017000021/https://www.artsbrookfield.com/event/snoopy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，又于圣迭戈、洛杉矶等全美主要城市巡展，10月1日结束<ref name= apparel/>。

2020年6月，她为华盛顿特区汉密尔顿酒店（Hamilton Hotel）职员设计制服，系Livelihood Collection品牌的分支<ref name= lily>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thelily.com/she-may-join-her-fathers-campaign-closer-to-2020-but-for-now-ashley-bidens-focused-on-economic-equality-and-hoodies/|title=She may join her father's campaign closer to 2020, but for now, Ashley Biden's focused on economic equality and hoodies|first=The Lily|last=News|website=thelily.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113193101/https://www.thelily.com/she-may-join-her-fathers-campaign-closer-to-2020-but-for-now-ashley-bidens-focused-on-economic-equality-and-hoodies/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name= Washington>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonian.com/2019/08/12/what-will-her-dads-campaign-mean-for-ashley-bidens-fashion-line/|title=What Will Her Dad's Campaign Mean for Ashley Biden's Fashion Line?|date=2019-08-12|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113193107/https://www.washingtonian.com/2019/08/12/what-will-her-dads-campaign-mean-for-ashley-bidens-fashion-line/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/2019/06/12/ashley-biden-knows-presidential-campaign-is-coming-now-shes-talking-hoodies-economic-inequality/|title=Ashley Biden knows a presidential campaign is coming. For now, she's talking hoodies and economic inequality.|first=Robin|last=Givhan|work=The Washington Post|date=2019-06-12|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912113951/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/2019/06/12/ashley-biden-knows-presidential-campaign-is-coming-now-shes-talking-hoodies-economic-inequality/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。制服在私人发布晚会上公布<ref name= Washington/>。酒店向Livelihood捐款1.5万美元<ref name= lily/><ref name= Washington/>。

== 个人生活 ==
