2002年，阿什莉在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]遭逮捕，被控妨碍警察<ref name= chicago>{{Cite web|last=services|first=Items compiled from Tribune news|title=Senator's daughter arrested in Chicago|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2002-08-04-0208040276-story.html|access-date=2020-10-17|website=Chicago Tribune|date=2002-08-04|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101103153/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2002-08-04-0208040276-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。那天晚上她正要离开{{tsl|en|Division Street|分区街}}一家酒吧的时候，朋友约翰·考伦蒂斯（John Kaulentis）和警察口角，朝对方扔了一罐汽水，当时这位警察要他远离阻止酒吧客人走到街道上的护栏<ref name= chicago/>。后来冲突升级，导致另一位朋友凯利·多诺霍（Kelly Donohoe）一位警察<ref name= chicago/>。就在考伦蒂斯和多诺霍被抓去的拘留时候，阿什莉因所谓的“口头恐吓”警察被捕<ref name= chicago/>。三人最终交{{tsl|en|recognizance|担保金}}获释<ref name= chicago/>。

2009年，阿什莉的朋友试图将她在派对上吸食[[可卡因|可卡因]]的影片卖给《[[纽约邮报|纽约邮报]]》，要价200万美元<ref name= hindu>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/world/joe-biden-s-daughter-caught-on-camera-snorting-cocaine/story-qozubVpTVctLgmIaWXrgZJ.html|title='Joe Biden's daughter caught on camera snorting Cocaine'|date=2009-03-30|website=Hindustan Times|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103235958/https://www.hindustantimes.com/world/joe-biden-s-daughter-caught-on-camera-snorting-cocaine/story-qozubVpTVctLgmIaWXrgZJ.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2002-aug-04-na-briefs4.1-story.html|title=Sen. Biden's Daughter Arrested in Altercation|date=2002-08-04|website=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119153442/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2002-aug-04-na-briefs4.1-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。经过协商，开价减到40万美元，但报社拒绝接受，改为发表一篇关于这段视频的报道<ref name= hindu/><ref name= vanity>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2009/03/ashley-biden-drugs-and-the-real-cause-for-outrage|title=Ashley Biden, Drugs, and the Real Cause for Outrage|first=Mike|last=Hogan|website=Vanity Fair|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225004839/http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2009/03/ashley-biden-drugs-and-the-real-cause-for-outrage|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《纽约邮报》报道发表后，有消息指阿什莉曾于1999年在[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]因持有[[大麻|大麻]]被捕，但控罪后来撤销，她也获释<ref name= vanity/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lawenforcementtoday.com/bidens-family-members-have-prior-arrests-yet-have-seen-no-jail-time/|title=Report: Joe Biden's family members have prior arrests for drugs and drunk driving. So why no jail time?|date=2020-07-12|website=Law Enforcement Today|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119153442/https://www.lawenforcementtoday.com/bidens-family-members-have-prior-arrests-yet-have-seen-no-jail-time/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年，阿什莉在哥哥博的介绍下，结识整形兼[[耳鼻喉科学|耳鼻喉]]外科医生{{tsl|en|Howard Krein|霍华德·凯林}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thelist.com/237917/the-truth-about-ashley-bidens-husband/|title=The truth about Ashley Biden's husband|first=Erin|last=Fenton|date=2020-08-18|website=TheList.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104153514/https://www.thelist.com/237917/the-truth-about-ashley-bidens-husband/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年，两人在{{le|布兰迪威尔圣约瑟夫教堂|St. Joseph on the Brandywine}}举行{{le|跨宗教婚姻|interfaith marriage|跨宗教婚礼}}（凯尔文信犹太教）<ref name= elle/><ref name= wedding/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/ashley-biden-marries-jewish-doctor-1.5169138|title=Ashley Biden, daughter of U.S. Vice President, marries Jewish doctor|website=Haaretz.com|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101071948/https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/ashley-biden-marries-jewish-doctor-1.5169138|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍华德在费城{{tsl|en|Thomas Jefferson University Hospital|托马斯·杰斐逊大学医院}}工作，担任{{tsl|en|Thomas Jefferson University|托马斯·杰斐逊大学}}面部、整形及重构手术助理教授<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/OTUS/meet-joe-bidens-future-son-law/story?id=16475464|title=Meet Joe Biden's Future Son-in-Law|website=ABC News|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106163827/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/OTUS/meet-joe-bidens-future-son-law/story?id=16475464|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

